<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CanLite Data Affirmation</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            color-scheme: dark;
            --bg: #071019;
            --panel: rgba(12, 22, 36, 0.92);
            --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --text: #eef4ff;
            --muted: rgba(238, 244, 255, 0.7);
            --accent: #8fd3ff;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            padding: 24px;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(69, 143, 255, 0.18), transparent 34%),
                linear-gradient(180deg, #08111a 0%, #050a10 100%);
            color: var(--text);
        }
        .card {
            width: min(100%, 760px);
            padding: 28px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            background: var(--panel);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            box-shadow: 0 30px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.34);
        }
        h1 { margin-top: 0; }
        p, li { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
        ul { padding-left: 20px; }
        .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 22px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        button {
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: #04110a;
            background: var(--accent);
        }
        a { color: var(--accent); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
    <h1>Confirm current data policy</h1>
    <p>Signed in as <strong><%= email %></strong>. Before continuing, you must affirm the current CanLite data handling policy dated <%= updatedAt %>.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>CanLite logs page visits and account/session activity.</li>
        <li>CanLite may associate visits, searches, ad impressions, and ad clicks with your account.</li>
        <li>CanLite may use those signals for affiliate selection, bidding, learning, measurement, and anti-abuse systems.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Read the full <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>.</p>
    <form method="post" action="/consent">
        <input type="hidden" name="returnTo" value="<%= returnTo %>">
        <div class="actions">
            <button type="submit">I affirm and continue</button>
            <a href="/privacy">Review policy again</a>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>
</body>
</html>
